bug #51559 [DependencyInjection] `#[Autowire]` attribute should have precedence over bindings (HypeMC)

This PR was merged into the 6.3 branch.

Discussion
----------

[DependencyInjection] `#[Autowire]` attribute should have precedence over bindings

| Q             | A
| ------------- | ---
| Branch?       | 6.3
| Bug fix?      | yes
| New feature?  | no
| Deprecations? | no
| Tickets       | Fix #49082
| License       | MIT
| Doc PR        | -

It seems logical (I think) that the `#[Autowire]` attribute has precedence over any bindings.
